<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 03 Jul 2024 12:24:21 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>英国大选：工党的外交政策计划是什么？</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/uk/uk-election-what-are-labours-foreign-policy-plans-2024-07-03/</link><description>英国工党预计将赢得周四的全国大选，在野14年后重新掌权，并任命凯尔·斯塔默(Keir Starmer)为英国新任首相。</description><pubDate>Wed, 03 Jul 2024 11:23:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/uk/uk-election-what-are-labours-foreign-policy-plans-2024-07-03/</guid></item><item><title>消息人士称，俄罗斯公司提高锌产量以满足政府需求</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/russian-firms-raise-zinc-output-meet-government-demand-sources-say-2024-07-03/</link><description>两位知情人士告诉路透社，俄罗斯企业在过去一个月提高了锌金属产量，以受益于国家需求的增长，并减少对中国作为材料目的地的依赖。</description><pubDate>Wed, 03 Jul 2024 11:04:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/russian-firms-raise-zinc-output-meet-government-demand-sources-say-2024-07-03/</guid></item><item><title>普华永道在监管审查中任命新中国区主管</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/pwc-names-new-china-head-amid-regulatory-scrutiny-2024-07-03/</link><description>普华永道 (PwC) 任命内部高管李彦宏为新任中国区主管，此举正值该公司面临中国大陆和香港金融监管机构的调查。</description><pubDate>Wed, 03 Jul 2024 10:48:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/pwc-names-new-china-head-amid-regulatory-scrutiny-2024-07-03/</guid></item><item><title>俄罗斯央行每日人民币掉期交易量创历史新高</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/russian-central-banks-daily-yuan-swap-volume-hits-record-high-2024-07-03/</link><description>数据显示，俄罗斯央行周三在货币互换交易中向银行提供了创纪录的195亿元人民币（26.8亿美元），因为在美元和欧元交易受到限制后，银行寻求其他方式来补充其外汇储备。</description><pubDate>Wed, 03 Jul 2024 10:43:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/russian-central-banks-daily-yuan-swap-volume-hits-record-high-2024-07-03/</guid></item><item><title>早间竞价：工作岗位扫描新纪录，特斯拉股价上涨</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-pix-2024-07-03/</link><description>迈克·多兰 (Mike Dolan) 对美国和全球市场未来一天的展望</description><pubDate>Wed, 03 Jul 2024 10:05:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-pix-2024-07-03/</guid></item><item><title>独家：印度官员参观富士康 iPhone 工厂，询问高管招聘事宜</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/indian-officials-visit-foxconn-iphone-plant-question-executives-about-hiring-2024-07-03/</link><description>在路透社报道苹果主要供应商拒绝已婚女性从事 iPhone 组装工作后，一名官员表示，印度劳工官员本周参观了该国南部的一家富士康工厂，并向高管询问了该公司的招聘做法。</description><pubDate>Wed, 03 Jul 2024 09:40:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/indian-officials-visit-foxconn-iphone-plant-question-executives-about-hiring-2024-07-03/</guid></item><item><title>消息人士称，德国阻止了大众燃气轮机业务向中国出售的计划</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/germany-blocks-planned-sale-vws-gas-turbine-business-china-sources-2024-07-03/</link><description>两位政府消息人士称，德国内阁周三阻止了大众汽车子公司曼能源解决方案公司燃气轮机部门向一家中国公司出售的计划。</description><pubDate>Wed, 03 Jul 2024 09:32:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/germany-blocks-planned-sale-vws-gas-turbine-business-china-sources-2024-07-03/</guid></item><item><title>北京与欧盟进行谈判，中国电动汽车制造商准备应对关税</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/china-ev-makers-brace-tariffs-beijing-eu-engage-talks-2024-07-03/</link><description>随着欧盟委员会对中国制造的电动汽车征收临时关税的时间紧迫，汽车制造商正准备迎接数十亿美元的新成本，分析师预计这些成本将减缓其在欧洲的扩张。</description><pubDate>Wed, 03 Jul 2024 09:32:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/china-ev-makers-brace-tariffs-beijing-eu-engage-talks-2024-07-03/</guid></item><item><title>降雨导致长江水位上涨，中国东部地区出现洪水担忧</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/flood-fears-chinas-east-rain-swells-yangtze-river-levels-2024-07-03/</link><description>中国南方强降雨导致长江水位上涨，促使下游东部地区为可能发生的洪水做好准备。</description><pubDate>Wed, 03 Jul 2024 09:25:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/flood-fears-chinas-east-rain-swells-yangtze-river-levels-2024-07-03/</guid></item><item><title>印度 莫迪与普京的莫斯科峰会被视为中国阴影下两国关系的关键</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/india-modis-moscow-summit-with-putin-seen-key-ties-chinas-shadow-2024-07-03/</link><description>分析人士表示，印度总理纳伦德拉·莫迪预计在几天内访问俄罗斯，这可能有助于打消人们的担忧，即新德里与西方过于接近，与莫斯科距离越来越远，从而将空间让给了中国。</description><pubDate>Wed, 03 Jul 2024 08:54:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/india-modis-moscow-summit-with-putin-seen-key-ties-chinas-shadow-2024-07-03/</guid></item><item><title>习主席表示中方支持哈萨克斯坦加入金砖国家</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china-supports-kazakhstan-joining-brics-president-xi-says-2024-07-03/</link><description>中国官方媒体周三报道称，中国国家主席习近平表示，他支持哈萨克斯坦加入金砖国家集团，因为这个发展中国家正在考虑进一步扩张，以与它认为已经过时的西方主导的世界秩序相抗衡。</description><pubDate>Wed, 03 Jul 2024 08:34:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china-supports-kazakhstan-joining-brics-president-xi-says-2024-07-03/</guid></item><item><title>联合国报告称中国在人工智能专利竞赛中处于领先地位</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/artificial-intelligence/china-leading-generative-ai-patents-race-un-report-says-2024-07-03/</link><description>联合国周三的数据显示，中国在聊天机器人等生成式人工智能发明方面远远领先于其他国家，申请的专利数量是最接近的竞争对手美国的六倍。</description><pubDate>Wed, 03 Jul 2024 08:06:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/artificial-intelligence/china-leading-generative-ai-patents-race-un-report-says-2024-07-03/</guid></item><item><title>外汇分析师表示，印度卢比兑人民币套利交易在美国大选结果之前仍将具有吸引力</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/india-rupee-chinese-yuan-carry-trade-hold-appeal-until-us-election-outcome-fx-2024-07-03/</link><description>交易员和外汇分析师表示，将世界上两个人口最多的国家的货币相互进行交易一直是套利交易者的热门选择，并且至少在今年晚些时候美国大选结果出来之前，这种吸引力将保持下去。</description><pubDate>Wed, 03 Jul 2024 07:48:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/india-rupee-chinese-yuan-carry-trade-hold-appeal-until-us-election-outcome-fx-2024-07-03/</guid></item><item><title>德国汽车业敦促欧盟降低对中国制造汽车的关税</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/german-car-industry-urges-eu-drop-tariffs-china-made-cars-2024-07-03/</link><description>德国汽车工业协会(VDA)敦促欧盟委员会取消对中国制造的电动汽车征收的关税，这是在关税周四生效之前影响谈判的最后努力。</description><pubDate>Wed, 03 Jul 2024 07:10:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/german-car-industry-urges-eu-drop-tariffs-china-made-cars-2024-07-03/</guid></item><item><title>随着贸易争端升级，欧盟各国政府对中国电动汽车关税犹豫不决</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/eu-governments-waver-over-chinese-ev-tariffs-trade-spat-escalates-2024-07-03/</link><description>欧盟国家在是否支持对中国制造的电动汽车征收额外关税的问题上犹豫不决，突显出布鲁塞尔在为其最大贸易案争取支持方面面临的挑战，而北京则威胁要进行大范围的报复。</description><pubDate>Wed, 03 Jul 2024 06:04:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/eu-governments-waver-over-chinese-ev-tariffs-trade-spat-escalates-2024-07-03/</guid></item></channel></rss>